{"data":{"items":[{"content":"{\"text\":\"因为人的手握笔，手掌总是有点往右倾斜的。写横的时候这个倾斜的力正好和写横的方向(往右)重合了，所以笔豪不会歪。写竖的时候手掌既做不到完全与纸面平行，也做不到完全与直面垂直，所以总会有多余的力让笔豪偏掉，并且笔杆在自然书写的过程中会有点微微右倾，这个也跟竖的方向不平衡(个人见解)。\",\"hasMore\":false}","createdTime":"2023-07-08T11:14:51+0800","evaluateStatus":0,"id":12897895,"userInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20230326/2023032604231141877946.jpg","ccUserName":"凶猛鹰","identity":0,"nickName":"银【0630】","userId":30311942},"userPower":0},{"content":"{\"text\":\"我用的笔比述古软一些，算是投机取巧而已😂\",\"hasMore\":false}","createdTime":"2023-07-08T08:32:40+0800","evaluateStatus":0,"id":12897566,"parentUserInfo":{"avatar":"https://i2n.hjfile.cn/u/200/133276406/9b72403ba54c47f.jpg","ccUserName":"陈秋杏2jdg6","identity":0,"nickName":"陈秋杏","userId":133276406},"userInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20231020/2023102006580863363416.jpg","ccUserName":"手机用户2873nyhgj","identity":0,"nickName":"東南隅【0530】","userId":164418225},"userPower":0},{"content":"{\"text\":\"起码比我的圆，哈哈\",\"hasMore\":false}","createdTime":"2023-07-08T08:24:07+0800","evaluateStatus":0,"id":12897564,"userInfo":{"avatar":"https://i2n.hjfile.cn/u/200/133276406/9b72403ba54c47f.jpg","ccUserName":"陈秋杏2jdg6","identity":0,"nickName":"陈秋杏","userId":133276406},"userPower":0},{"content":"{\"text\":\"就是聚锋之后笔毛会有点弧度 一边瘦一点一边胖一点\",\"hasMore\":false}","createdTime":"2023-07-08T08:10:58+0800","evaluateStatus":0,"id":12897552,"parentUserInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20231020/2023102006580863363416.jpg","ccUserName":"手机用户2873nyhgj","identity":0,"nickName":"東南隅【0530】","userId":164418225},"userInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20230312/2023031208242014075300.jpg","ccUserName":"手机用户0496viktz","identity":0,"nickName":"太阳当空赵【0464】","userId":154250449},"userPower":0},{"content":"{\"text\":\"直直的圆锥是什么意思？\",\"hasMore\":false}","createdTime":"2023-07-08T08:08:30+0800","evaluateStatus":0,"id":12897627,"parentUserInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20230312/2023031208242014075300.jpg","ccUserName":"手机用户049